1
00:00:48,399 --> 00:00:49,920
Including this piece of equipment,

2
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:50,880
they're all brand new.

3
00:00:50,920 --> 00:00:51,880
We just brought them in, Mr. Ma.

4
00:00:52,159 --> 00:00:53,119
The problem's already fixed.

5
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,280
One of the parts was broken.

6
00:00:54,399 --> 00:00:55,479
Luckily, we had one in the factory.

7
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:56,759
We've already replaced it for them.

8
00:00:57,719 --> 00:00:58,399
Thank you!

9
00:00:59,079 --> 00:00:59,759
That's amazing!

10
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:01,479
You saved my life!

11
00:01:03,679 --> 00:01:05,480
Why does this engineer

12
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:06,400
look so familiar?

13
00:01:06,439 --> 00:01:07,200
He's the one from that day,

14
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:08,560
number 19 on the field.

15
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:09,439
Lu Donglin.

16
00:01:09,519 --> 00:01:10,120
Engineer Lu!

17
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:12,560
You're incredible!

18
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:15,200
Dear Lu,

19
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,599
I'm a fan of yours.

20
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:18,239
Now I'm a fan of you as a person too.

21
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:19,400
Ma!

22
00:01:19,799 --> 00:01:21,959
I must email headquarters right away.

23
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:23,680
I need to increase the investment,

24
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:24,760
build a factory complex,

25
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:25,799
form a strategic partnership!

26
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:26,519
Great!

27
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:27,560
Lu,

28
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,040
can I take a photo with you?

29
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:30,439
No problem, of course!

30
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:31,120
Come on.

31
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:33,879
Together now, smile!

32
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:36,480
One, two, three!

33
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,840
Getting married?

34
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:49,480
You're taking leave to get married now?

35
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,560
I didn't choose this timing.

36
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,599
My wedding date

37
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,239
was set long ago.

38
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:55,840
Bullshit!

39
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:56,599
You son of a...

40
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,239
Zhou Hang,

41
00:01:59,359 --> 00:02:01,519
you only managed one draw,

42
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:02,920
and now you want to hold a wedding?

43
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:04,640
If word got out about this,

44
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,200
how would that look?

45
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,040
Even if you'd scored

46
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,719
just one goal!

47
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,840
I-I've already booked the venue.

48
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,039
Six months ago, I notified all

49
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:14,919
my friends and family.

50
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:16,400
I don't care.

51
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,560
You go tell him.

52
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,000
If he agrees,

53
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:20,280
I won't have any problem with it.

54
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,120
Can I have one day?

55
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:30,319
Just half a day.

56
00:02:31,759 --> 00:02:32,719
After the wedding banquet at noon,

57
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:33,479
I'll come straight back to the team.

58
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,800
I promise it won't affect training.

59
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:35,439
Coach,

60
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,879
Xue Hua and her parents understand.

61
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:40,240
They've all said

62
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,400
we'll keep the banquet simple.

63
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:48,680
Just treat it as a wedding for good luck.

64
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:30,280
Xue Hua!

65
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:31,960
I love you!

66
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,840
Okay, okay!

67
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:35,879
Hang,

68
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,520
With such a beautiful bride,

69
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:39,280
can you bear to rejoin the team tonight?

70
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:42,159
Get outta here, stop messing around!

71
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,520
Hang,

72
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,520
You'd better step up tonight.

73
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,560
Can't score a zero, you know.

74
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,719
You brat, what do you know?

75
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:50,240
Don't mess with me!

76
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,599
Stop it, stop it!

77
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,520
I, Zhou Hang,

78
00:03:59,439 --> 00:03:59,879
well,

79
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,319
am not great with words,

80
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,520
but today I just have to say this.

81
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:07,479
I must have built up

82
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:09,759
so much good karma in my past life

83
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,479
Or I'm blessed across three lifetimes

84
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,560
for me in this life

85
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:17,120
to be able to hold you.

86
00:04:25,199 --> 00:04:25,879
Zhou Hang,

87
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,600
you know what?

88
00:04:28,199 --> 00:04:30,120
The first time I saw you, drenched in sweat,

89
00:04:30,279 --> 00:04:31,839
making the kids laugh,

90
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:33,560
I thought right then

91
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,439
that you're such a responsible

92
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,279
and lovely person.

93
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,600
Later,

94
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,040
when you went to train

95
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,720
and got all covered in bruises,

96
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,079
I saw it all.

97
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,199
The way you fought so hard

98
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:48,680
for your dream and your duty

99
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,199
was just incredibly cool.

100
00:04:50,839 --> 00:04:51,439
So,

101
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:52,680
from now on,

102
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:54,000
you look after the team,

103
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:55,720
and I'll look after you.

104
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:59,160
Yes, yes, yes!

105
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:09,079
Kiss, kiss, kiss!

106
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,240
Here we go!

107
00:05:11,399 --> 00:05:13,279
Three, two...

108
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,720
Three, two, one!

109
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:27,000
Cheese!

110
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,839
Changzhou FC!

111
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:34,560
Awesome!

112
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:38,319
Thank you!

113
00:05:40,879 --> 00:05:41,839
It's about time.

114
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,279
I need to take them back to training.

115
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:44,680
Congratulations, congratulations!

116
00:05:44,759 --> 00:05:45,839
Thanks, Coach! Thanks, Coach!

117
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:46,480
Congratulations!

118
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,240
Bye, Coach!

119
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:47,639
Bye-bye!

120
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,319
Goodbye, Coach!

121
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:48,879
Bye, Sis Yan!

122
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,879
Guys, can you believe this?

123
00:06:43,279 --> 00:06:44,920
Right after the wedding,

124
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:46,480
we're seamlessly transitioning

125
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,519
back to closed-door training.

126
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,319
Should I give you a separate day off?

127
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,319
No, no, no! Coach, Coach!

128
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:53,920
Don't, don't!

129
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:58,279
Stop, stop, stop, stop!

130
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:03,399
Coach,

131
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,759
Zhou Hang requesting to rejoin the team!

132
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:05,920
So soon?

133
00:07:07,319 --> 00:07:08,560
Xue Hua kicked me out.

134
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:09,600
She said

135
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:11,160
watching you guys head to training,

136
00:07:11,279 --> 00:07:12,360
my heart had already flown off.

137
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,319
She didn't want to be the bad guy.

138
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,879
Said the honeymoon can wait,

139
00:07:15,079 --> 00:07:16,079
and I can spend a lifetime

140
00:07:16,439 --> 00:07:17,040
slowly paying it back.

141
00:07:18,519 --> 00:07:19,560
Sis is the best!

142
00:07:20,199 --> 00:07:20,839
Netizens are saying

143
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,879
this is the ultimate wedding for good luck

144
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:23,920
Once that luck kicks in,

145
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,360
nothing can stop the goals from coming.

146
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:26,319
You bet!

147
00:07:27,079 --> 00:07:27,800
Changzhou FC!

148
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,319
Awesome!

149
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,319
Driver,

150
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:35,480
let's go!

151
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:49,639
What's wrong?

152
00:07:51,519 --> 00:07:53,040
At the wedding today,

153
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,279
seeing Zhou Hang and his wife,

154
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:54,879
got you jealous, huh?

155
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,519
Not really.

156
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:58,879
Don't get annoyed with me,

157
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:01,120
but I think Lu Yao's a great girl.

158
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,600
Look, at the wedding today,

159
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,639
she glanced at you a hundred times.

160
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,439
You didn't look at her once!

161
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,439
What if Lu Yao

162
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,360
finds someone else out there?

163
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,800
You'll regret it when it's too late.

164
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,120
You're like Tang Sanzang,

165
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:10,920
nag, nag, nag.

166
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:11,879
Will you ever stop?

167
00:08:15,319 --> 00:08:15,879
Brother,

168
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,079
take some advice from me.

169
00:08:18,519 --> 00:08:19,639
You're not getting any younger.

170
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:20,879
It's time to settle down.

171
00:09:16,879 --> 00:09:17,840
Girls, remember this.

172
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:20,120
What men fear isn't your crying,

173
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,159
it's you suddenly disappearing.

174
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,440
When he realizes

175
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,759
you're really leaving,

176
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:27,240
only then will he see your worth.

177
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:49,399
Yaoyao,

178
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:52,000
Aunt Zhang set you up with a guy.

179
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:54,000
Master's degree from overseas,

180
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,440
owns a place in the new district.

181
00:09:56,159 --> 00:09:58,279
Meet him tomorrow at lunch.

182
00:10:08,159 --> 00:10:09,000
The two teams are

183
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,399
being led by the referees,

184
00:10:10,519 --> 00:10:12,080
slowly walking onto the field.

185
00:10:13,759 --> 00:10:14,279
On screen,

186
00:10:14,279 --> 00:10:16,480
we see familiar old faces,

187
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:18,639
and quite a few new ones too.

188
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:21,440
Soon, as the match unfolds,

189
00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:23,200
we'll walk you through

190
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,320
the subtle adjustments

191
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:27,519
both teams made to today's starting lineups.

192
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,720
So, Miss Lu, you work at a TV station.

193
00:10:38,759 --> 00:10:40,600
I also follow the media regularly,

194
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,200
especially BBC

195
00:10:42,279 --> 00:10:43,879
and CNN's international coverage.

196
00:10:46,399 --> 00:10:48,039
Maybe I've been away too long,

197
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,159
but since coming back,

198
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,240
I really can't quite adjust.

199
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,360
Especially these days,

200
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,399
young people in China

201
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:55,879
live way too comfortably.

202
00:10:56,759 --> 00:10:57,960
When I was in Silicon Valley,

203
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,360
I worked 16 hours a day,

204
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,200
and still made time

205
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,279
to stay in shape,

206
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:03,759
hitting the gym,

207
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:04,759
playing ball,

208
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:05,919
running marathons.

209
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:08,879
Miss Lu, do you like sports?

210
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:09,879
A little bit.

211
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,960
If you're into fitness,

212
00:11:12,159 --> 00:11:13,240
I can be your personal trainer.

213
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,000
I've been training for over ten years,

214
00:11:16,799 --> 00:11:18,320
and the fitness meals I cook

215
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,200
are incredibly delicious,

216
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,919
on par with a three-star Michelin chef.

217
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:21,679
Playing at home,

218
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:23,519
wearing the red match kit,

219
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,039
in the first half,

220
00:11:24,039 --> 00:11:26,480
attacking from screen left to right.

221
00:11:26,559 --> 00:11:27,320
Watch the back post!

222
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,120
Wearing white tops

223
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:29,799
and black shorts,

224
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:30,480
in the first half,

225
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,039
attacking from screen right to left.

226
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,039
Have some water.

227
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:41,759
You know, I'm someone

228
00:11:41,759 --> 00:11:43,159
who's very picky about food.

229
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,440
Since coming back to Changzhou,

230
00:11:44,759 --> 00:11:46,440
I've tried every restaurant in town.

231
00:11:46,879 --> 00:11:47,600
Only this place's

232
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:48,639
grilled salmon

233
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:49,440
is actually decent.

234
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:50,279
Try some.

235
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:03,039
So Miss Lu likes soccer?

236
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,519
I'm usually way too busy,

237
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:06,879
so I don't have the time or energy

238
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:07,600
to spend on soccer.

239
00:12:07,879 --> 00:12:08,399
Let's be honest,

240
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,639
it's just a bunch of losers

241
00:12:10,759 --> 00:12:12,080
watching rich guys kick a ball.

242
00:12:12,399 --> 00:12:13,159
Especially these kinds of,

243
00:12:13,919 --> 00:12:15,279
you know, regional whatever

244
00:12:15,279 --> 00:12:16,000
leagues.

245
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,320
It's honestly just ridiculous.

246
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:20,240
Back in Silicon Valley,

247
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,279
my friend and I own a shooting range.

248
00:12:23,039 --> 00:12:23,639
I can take you there sometime

249
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:24,399
so you can try it out.

250
00:12:24,559 --> 00:12:26,840
Especially our live ammo,

251
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,639
the recoil when you fire it...

252
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:29,399
I mean, I'm...

253
00:12:29,399 --> 00:12:29,960
Excuse me.

254
00:12:30,559 --> 00:12:32,200
Could you turn the volume up, please?

255
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:39,639
What does your father do?

256
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:40,759
He's a businessman.

257
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,600
My father's a businessman too.

258
00:12:43,519 --> 00:12:44,919
He wants me to become a businessman,

259
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:46,840
but I have my own dream.

260
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,039
I want to be an actor.

261
00:12:49,919 --> 00:12:50,840
My idol is

262
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,200
Stanislavski.

263
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:53,720
A lot of Hollywood stars

264
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,480
are friends of mine.

265
00:12:55,399 --> 00:12:56,759
Lots of Oscar winners, too.

266
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,159
If you'd like to meet them,

267
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:58,639
I can introduce you.

268
00:12:58,639 --> 00:12:59,480
Excuse me.

269
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:00,799
Could you please turn the volume

270
00:13:00,799 --> 00:13:01,840
up a bit more, okay?

271
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:12,080
That's clearly a foul

272
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:14,320
that denied a goal-scoring opportunity.

273
00:13:14,399 --> 00:13:15,840
So the referee gave a straight red.

274
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:16,960
No issue with that call.

275
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:22,960
Hurry up and eat something.

276
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:23,720
It'll get cold soon.

277
00:13:24,519 --> 00:13:25,639
You eat first, you go ahead.

278
00:13:43,759 --> 00:13:44,559
I know doing this

279
00:13:44,559 --> 00:13:45,600
isn't exactly a real job.

280
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,120
Even if we win the Jiangsu Super League,

281
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,320
it won't really bring much.

282
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,039
But Yaoyao,

283
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:55,759
this is the last time

284
00:13:55,759 --> 00:13:56,679
in my life,

285
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,679
and the only time,

286
00:13:59,759 --> 00:14:01,000
I'll be this close to my dream.

287
00:14:03,639 --> 00:14:05,200
Actually, I think we

288
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:07,120
still share a lot of common interests.

289
00:14:07,279 --> 00:14:08,919
The referee's long whistle

290
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,399
signals the end

291
00:14:10,399 --> 00:14:11,480
of the match.

292
00:14:11,679 --> 00:14:12,639
Congratulations to the Yancheng Team

293
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,759
for taking all three points at home.

294
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:16,200
And best wishes to Changzhou FC.

295
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:18,000
Though their small goals of scoring one,

296
00:14:18,039 --> 00:14:18,720
getting one point,

297
00:14:18,759 --> 00:14:20,759
and winning one match weren't achieved,

298
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:22,000
the players still

299
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:24,080
showed an inspiring fighting spirit.

300
00:14:24,279 --> 00:14:24,759
We look forward to

301
00:14:24,799 --> 00:14:26,879
their breakthrough coming soon.

302
00:14:27,759 --> 00:14:29,080
We can work out together from now on,

303
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:31,080
shoot, play ball, do sports together,

304
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,240
and travel together.

305
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,440
A bunch of losers,

306
00:14:41,879 --> 00:14:43,519
a bunch of amateur athletes,

307
00:14:43,559 --> 00:14:44,360
making up a total joke.

308
00:14:44,679 --> 00:14:45,720
With that kind of level,

309
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,320
they shouldn't embarrass themselves.

310
00:14:48,039 --> 00:14:48,679
0-5.

311
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,600
Back when I played in high school,

312
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:51,399
I played better than them.

313
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:53,120
Especially their captain,

314
00:14:54,879 --> 00:14:55,480
Li Xiaoyong.

315
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:57,039
That video of his own goal,

316
00:14:57,039 --> 00:14:57,639
I saw it.

317
00:14:57,759 --> 00:14:59,840
He's just a complete idiot.

318
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:00,799
He really is...

319
00:15:00,799 --> 00:15:01,399
Mr. Chen,

320
00:15:02,279 --> 00:15:03,279
do you know that the idiot

321
00:15:03,279 --> 00:15:04,120
you're talking about,

322
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:05,840
to save an old worker,

323
00:15:06,639 --> 00:15:08,039
fell from a scaffolding

324
00:15:08,519 --> 00:15:09,720
and almost lost his leg?

325
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:11,360
And do you know he gets up

326
00:15:11,399 --> 00:15:12,559
at five every morning

327
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:14,440
to make breakfast for his mother,

328
00:15:14,919 --> 00:15:16,360
and then heads to training?

329
00:15:16,399 --> 00:15:17,480
Did you also know

330
00:15:17,679 --> 00:15:18,960
that for this competition,

331
00:15:19,519 --> 00:15:20,840
he turned down a job opportunity,

332
00:15:21,519 --> 00:15:22,399
and even gave up

333
00:15:22,399 --> 00:15:23,200
his own girlfriend?

334
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:30,720
Yes,

335
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,399
they didn't play well.

336
00:15:33,879 --> 00:15:35,159
They lost the match.

337
00:15:35,559 --> 00:15:37,440
But they dared to stand on that field.

338
00:15:37,679 --> 00:15:39,480
They dared to fight for this city.

339
00:15:40,679 --> 00:15:41,360
And you?

340
00:15:41,879 --> 00:15:44,279
You only brag about your golf,

341
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,399
your tennis,

342
00:15:45,559 --> 00:15:46,360
your sixteen hours

343
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,679
in Silicon Valley.

344
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:49,279
What else would you do

345
00:15:49,279 --> 00:15:49,799
for this city?

346
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,159
Loser.

347
00:15:58,919 --> 00:15:59,639
So classless.

348
00:16:03,679 --> 00:16:04,480
Have something to eat.

349
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:18,720
I know deep down

350
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:19,720
you've got a lot bottled up.

351
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:22,759
I was sitting in the stands yesterday,

352
00:16:23,159 --> 00:16:24,120
watching you on the sideline,

353
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:25,840
shouting until your voice went hoarse.

354
00:16:27,399 --> 00:16:28,240
The players fought till the very end,

355
00:16:28,399 --> 00:16:29,200
never letting up.

356
00:16:29,519 --> 00:16:30,879
That means it wasn't all for nothing.

357
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:36,159
Don't carry it all alone.

358
00:16:36,879 --> 00:16:38,120
If you want to talk tactics,

359
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:38,879
I'm listening.

360
00:16:39,279 --> 00:16:40,519
If you don't feel like talking,

361
00:16:41,039 --> 00:16:41,840
let's go catch a movie.

362
00:16:41,919 --> 00:16:42,399
How about it?

363
00:16:44,759 --> 00:16:45,919
No need. I'm fine.

364
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,120
No matter what,

365
00:16:56,559 --> 00:16:57,600
in my eyes you're

366
00:16:57,679 --> 00:16:58,759
the greatest head coach.

367
00:17:01,519 --> 00:17:03,240
Don't put pressure on yourself, okay?

368
00:17:03,799 --> 00:17:04,400
Just win one game,

369
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:05,599
and everything will be fine.

370
00:17:15,319 --> 00:17:16,039
Old buddy,

371
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,079
back then, you and I

372
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:19,720
fought countless times

373
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,079
over the kids playing football.

374
00:17:22,119 --> 00:17:24,400
I used to say kids who play football

375
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:25,440
won't amount to anything.

376
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:28,160
But now the Jiangsu Super League's blown up,

377
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:30,200
and Changzhou FC's matches,

378
00:17:30,559 --> 00:17:32,079
I haven't missed a single one.

379
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:34,480
Watching those kids now,

380
00:17:34,759 --> 00:17:36,640
fighting through game after game,

381
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:37,559
suddenly

382
00:17:37,559 --> 00:17:39,160
I understood why you held on.

383
00:17:39,839 --> 00:17:40,640
I think

384
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:42,960
those kids are amazing,

385
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,720
and so are you.

386
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:47,880
Losing really stings,

387
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:51,079
but that never-give-up spirit out there

388
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:52,599
moves people more

389
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:53,920
than any victory ever could.

390
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:57,440
At our age,

391
00:17:58,319 --> 00:18:01,039
health and happiness matter most.

392
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:02,160
I know.

393
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:04,640
I know how much pressure you're under.

394
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:05,920
Take it easy.

395
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:08,480
We're all standing with you.

396
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:11,480
You've already done great.

397
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:13,480
Win or lose,

398
00:18:13,559 --> 00:18:14,319
it's okay, it's okay.

399
00:18:14,519 --> 00:18:15,759
I'll keep on

400
00:18:15,759 --> 00:18:17,359
cheering you on.

401
00:18:17,759 --> 00:18:19,079
Best of luck.
